constraint.SQL:
["tIB_XMXX.XMLX={0} 
and tIB_XMXX.ID in (
select t1.XMMC 
from lcIB_NHSP t1 
where t1.instid in (select id from jgcrm.os_wfentry t2 where t2.state=4) 
) 
and tIB_XMXX.SSBM in (
SELECT t3.id FROM jgcrm.Lborganization t3
where 1=1 
start with t3.id ={1} connect by prior t3.id = t3.fid
)",[{"expression":"XMLX2","scale":0,"length":0,"type":1},{"expression":"$Login.User.OrgID","scale":0,"length":0,"type":1}]]

column.name: YJFXSL2
column.expression: <%@ livebos language='javascript' %> ABS_SQLVALUE("select YJFXGS from ECIF.lcIB_NHSP where XMMC=? and rownum = 1 order by instid desc",[XMMC2])

column.name: YJCZE2
column.expression: <%@ livebos language='javascript' %> ABS_SQLVALUE("select t1.MJZJ from ecif.lcIB_NHSP t1 where t1.XMMC=? and rownum = 1 order by instid desc",[XMMC2])

column.name: QNSHLR2
column.expression: <%@ livebos language='javascript' %> ABS_SQLVALUE("select (t1.YJCXSR+t1.YJBJSR) from ecif.lcIB_NHSP t1 where t1.XMMC=? and rownum = 1 order by instid desc",[XMMC2])
